summary: The document is a National Agency Check (NAC) request form for George Kaczmarczyk, associated with the USA Advanced Weapons Support Command, detailing his birth in Bomblitz, West Germany, service, and a favorable security determination. It also notes his relatives' alien registration details, highlighting foreign connections. The form, dated November 17, 1971, was marked 'UNCLASSIFIED' and released with deletions on March 9, 1995.
key_findings: The document is part of a security check process for George Kaczmarczyk, dated November 17, 1971.
It indicates a favorable security determination for Kaczmarczyk, with no adverse findings.
The form includes personal details such as place of birth (Bomblitz, West Germany), service number, and mentions of his relatives' alien registration details.
The document is marked as 'UNCLASSIFIED' and was released with deletions on March 9, 1995.
